{"tid":1785872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"任何藍變黃都係好事，就算係做樣都得，但係要有野睇唔可以得把口(文極長)","createTime":"2019-12-16T17:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T07:59:59.000Z","uid":295459,"like":65,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"1276974c12ec9af586181f809622f3d63645246b","tid":1785872,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:06:44.000Z","msg":"想講好多野，但係因為P牌，所以唯有係一個PO內講完<br />\n主要想講:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 接受藍轉黃/藍扮黃嘅思維(個人意見)<br />\n2. 如何用最簡單方法分辨可唔可以幫襯</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一點：接受藍轉黃/藍扮黃嘅思維</span></span></strong><br />\n狗嘅暴行而家好多好多人都睇唔過眼<br />\n好多人係因為見到721，831呢種恐怖襲擊<br />\n先至由藍轉黃，又或者係由港豬轉黃<br />\n咁如果假設一個人，佢係721前講左支持警察嘅野，721之後屌狗呢？<br />\n呢種好明顯係因為721呢件事令到佢轉變左，佢係藍轉黃，而唔係咩扮黃<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">至於佢點解轉變，原因可以有好多</span><br />\n我住深藍區，識有人係因為721變黃，有人831變黃<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有老野831過左都係藍，但係見到呀婆跪係到比狗推落地之後變左深黃</span></strong><br />\n點解轉變係好難講，總知一樣超越左佢接受範圍嘅野出現左，佢就忽然會轉變<br />\n頭先見到個PO: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1785368/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1785368/page/1</a><br />\n點解大家都覺得呢位呀叔好? 睇得出佢係呢場運動前都係港豬<br />\n就係因為佢轉變左，同理亦都可以應用係店主身上<br />\n<br />\n至於藍扮黃，就姐係明明店主到目前都仲係撐警<br />\n但就扮哂支持運動咁樣，引港人幫襯。<br />\n事實上呢樣野係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">值得支持</span><br />\n因為我地唔係神，冇可能睇穿店主唸乜野<br />\n以第三者角度，只可以睇得出佢係黃<br />\n而佢亦都係一個榜樣，做比D藍絲睇<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拿，而家你擺明撐運動屌政府嘅，咁就有生意</span></span></strong><br />\n想搵錢？屌政府囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假設佢真係藍扮黃，佢嘅事就會被傳出去<br />\n更多藍會扮黃<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">到時就會成個場都係黃</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第二點：如何用最簡單方法分辨可唔可以幫襯</span></span></strong><br />\n兩隻字：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">宣傳</span></span>，總知有宣傳支援示威嘅，幫襯<br />\n唔好講咩店長唸乜，店員唸乜<br />\n我地唔係神，唔知佢地實際上點唸<br />\n總知：間鋪有宣傳示威嘅，幫襯<br />\n例如：有文宣，或者有播榮光，或者有連儂牆，或者有紙屌狗<br />\n我要直接見到或者聽到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>唔好同我講間店店主係黃，但係成間鋪連張文宣都冇，我係唔會信</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n相反，幫襯嘅密度同力度，最好同佢嘅支持度成正比<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">例如一間野得文宣就是但得閒買一兩次<br />\n但係另一間有文宣又播榮光，仲要得閒鳩叫口號，一定係瘋狂制裁</span></strong><br />\n要有實實在在嘅支持，我要睇到聽到，唔要得把口支持<br />\n呢樣正正就係做到我想講<br />\n總知撐示威有生意，撐警拍烏鷹出現<br />\n想搵錢？屌政府囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍絲冇腦架，間鋪冇文宣但係有人幫襯，佢唔會知點解<br />\n間鋪文宣愈多，就愈多人幫襯，佢就會明點解，ＯＫ？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">同意唔該幫手推推<br />\n我P牌推唔到</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"34c9cd56d6146bf70771e71293a48324afc084ee","tid":1785872,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人幫手推"},{"pid":"0b634fbe588cb35faad7623736fdbb6c1658b753","tid":1785872,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34c9cd56d6146bf70771e71293a48324afc084ee","tid":1785872,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人幫手推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:09:55.000Z","msg":"幫你"},{"pid":"fecf67c710889db96e2c4e14824c6a5e9929aa9e","tid":1785872,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b634fbe588cb35faad7623736fdbb6c1658b753","tid":1785872,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34c9cd56d6146bf70771e71293a48324afc084ee","tid":1785872,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人幫手推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:09:55.000Z","msg":"幫你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:10:36.000Z","msg":"THANKS<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4a4f9de9aa3adb2eb809e827b318f6121ac350","tid":1785872,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:11:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4dbe134d54937f7ae6cfaf41f624e26a6136bf0d","tid":1785872,"uid":295459,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"大J單野<br />\n已經搞到太複雜<br />\n直接D 叫大J呀哥貼到成間鋪都係文宣<br />\n唔係就唔幫襯<br />\n我自7,8月開始都睇緊大J<br />\n但係J大呀哥間野<br />\n我真係不了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcee247f292fa45e33c8dc20bae3548c1026780f","tid":1785872,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"